trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: EditorPartDesigner is a public implementation of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.PartDesigner> base class for the purpose of rendering <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls at design time.
trans-unit.target: EditorPartDesigner er en offentlig implementering av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.PartDesigner>basisklasse hensikten gjengivelse <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller under utformingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.PartDesigner>

trans-unit.source: It adds the capability of carrying zone information from the associated control into design view, but does not otherwise change the functionality of the parent control.
trans-unit.target: Den legger til muligheten til å utføre zone-informasjon fra den tilknyttede kontrollen til utformingsvisning, men ikke ellers endres ikke funksjonaliteten til den overordnede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: As with other control designers, you can change the design-time rendering of custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls by inheriting from EditorPartDesigner and overriding the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Som med andre kontroll-utviklere kan du endre utformingen gjengivelse av egendefinerte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller ved arving fra EditorPartDesigner og overstyrer den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: If you want to override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A> method, be sure to include the base implementation so as to retain zone information.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil overstyre den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A>metoden, må du ta base implementeringen å beholde informasjon om.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Creates a copy of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control to render at design time.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en kopi av det tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontrollen skal gjengi ved utformingen.

trans-unit.source: This method is overridden to copy zone information to the view control.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden overstyres for å kopiere informasjon om til visningskontrollen.

trans-unit.source: A copy of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: En kopi av det tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Verifies that the control resides in a zone of type <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase"></xref>, and then gets the markup that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Bekrefter at kontrollen befinner seg i en sone av typen <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase"> </xref>, og henter markup som brukes til å representere kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The markup that is used to represent the control at design time, or error markup if the control does not reside in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Koden som brukes til å representere kontrollen under utformingen eller feil markup Hvis kontrollen ikke finnes i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Binding designer til det tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control associated with the designer.
